OL,3,CHottest-ever start to Wimbledon with
OL,4,C29.7C recorded
OL,6,FThis year's Wimbledon tennis
OL,7,Fchampionships has begun with the
OL,8,Fhottest opening day on record,
OL,9,Faccording to the Met Office.
OL,11,FTemperatures reached a provisional
OL,12,Fhigh of 29.7C at Kew Gardens in west
OL,13,FLondon on Monday afternoon, surpassing
OL,14,Fthe previous record of 29.3C set in
OL,15,FJune 2001.
OL,17,FSpectators queued from the early hours
OL,18,Fto enter the All England Club in south-
OL,19,Fwest London, with many using fans,
OL,20,Fumbrellas and sunscreen to cope with
OL,21,Fthe heat.
