OL,6,FVicki Broad, 57, a retired nurse from
OL,7,FSwansea, who was the first person in
OL,8,Fthe queue, said: "The sun has been
OL,9,Ftough but we're in the shade now."
OL,11,FPaul Jackson, from Stockport, told the
OL,12,FPA news agency: "We were a bit worried
OL,13,Fabout the heat, but it's been
OL,14,Fmanageable."
OL,16,F"We've been drinking water, wearing
OL,17,Fhats, and making the most of the
OL,18,Fshade."
